title: Death in Yellowstone by Lee Whittleley.mobi
description:
Death in Yellowstone: Accidents and Foolhardiness in the First National Park

Requested by Mimi369

By Lee H. Whittlesey

Published by Roberts Rinehart in 1995

Tags: nonfiction, nature

MOBI, 240 pages, English (1570980217)


Intriguing stories of how people have died in Yellowstone warn about the many dangers that exist there and in wild areas in general.
